                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/1700.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-05-08T12:00:00-04:40">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 8, 1915—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>President Jiménes informed me today that Government anticipates several small
                    disturbances as forerunner of revolution. He added that steps are being taken to
                    apprehend leaders and arrests will be made today.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sullivan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
